# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Robinhood Pair Tracker — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your own values.
#  Never commit .env.local to version control.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Wallet Connection ─────────────────────────────────────────
# At least ONE provider is needed for wallet connect to work.

# Privy App ID — for embedded wallet (email / Google login).
# Get yours at https://dashboard.privy.io → Apps → App ID
# When empty, the email/Google login option is hidden.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID=clm_abc123...

# Reown (AppKit) Project ID — for external wallets (MetaMask,
# Rabby, WalletConnect, etc.).
# Get yours at https://reown.com/dashboard → Projects → Project ID
# When empty, the external-wallet option is hidden.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_REOWN_PROJECT_ID=abc123...

# ── Robinhood Chain RPC ───────────────────────────────────────
# An Alchemy API key is recommended for on-chain reads (portfolio
# balances, token info, swap quotes).
# Default fallback (unauthenticated, rate-limited):
#   https://robinhood-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RH_RPC_URL=https://robinhood-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_ALCHEMY_KEY

# ── App URL ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by Reown AppKit metadata and some external links.
# Default: https://robinhoodscreener.vercel.app
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ── Data Sources (optional) ───────────────────────────────────
# Most sources work without keys, but Birdeye and CoinMarketCap
# require an API key for enriched data.

# Birdeye API key — Free Standard plan.
# Get yours at https://birdeye.so/api
# When empty, Birdeye data is skipped.
# BIRDEYE_API_KEY=abc123...

# CoinMarketCap API key — Free Basic plan (333 calls/day).
# Get yours at https://pro.coinmarketcap.com
# When empty, CoinMarketCap data is skipped.
# COINMARKETCAP_API_KEY=abc123...
